#: C/evolution.xml:342(para)
msgid ""
"If you selected Novell GroupWise, IMAP, POP, or USENET News as your server, "
"you need to specify additional information."
msgstr ""
"如果您选择 Novell GroupWise，IMAP, POP, or USENET News 作为您的服务器，您需要"
